parameters.name: END_TIME
parameters.description:
End time column. This field contains time in PDS format                 
      yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss.sssZ. The individual elements of                    
      the time field can be read using the format                             
      (i4,4(1x,i2),1x,f6.3) yr, mon, day, hr, min, sec.
